{"tid":1569644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇求下咁多位，俾啲堅持","createTime":"2019-09-14T16:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T16:56:46.000Z","uid":315785,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d17521341c034079a474ec267ce9d5f9c7790f28","tid":1569644,"uid":315785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:39:21.000Z","msg":"自從林鄭條八婆講咗撤回之後，肯出去發夢嘅人真係少咗一大節，我明白有啲人已經收貨，大家亦要返工返學，但係問下自己，而家我地真係贏咗啦咩?說好的五大訴求呢，再且你見住啲後生仔俾警察藍絲咁亂咁拉亂咁打，不時又見到女仔俾人非禮，你真係忍心過表面安逸嘅生活咩? 我求下你丫，出黎行下街好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我自己都讀緊勁忙嘅科，讀得唔好係真係會整死人，但係我選擇聽日一路行街一路溫，而唔係話「發夢?不了，要溫書。」求下大家俾多啲堅持耐性，最好就叫埋身邊班fd一齊黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日3點希望大家可以係銅鑼灣陪我溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab495cfad7bc3e40b717c54172c512caaf87c7f","tid":1569644,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1veB7Va.jpg&h=d08508ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a57ee600038d272389a18c22d67f9c2a3aac81d2","tid":1569644,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:49:28.000Z","msg":"日本南北朝時代的武將楠木正成將軍壯烈犧牲後，旗幟上留有「非、理、法、權、天」五個字。這五個字是什麼意思呢？<br />\n<br />\n非，就是不對的事情。所以，「非」不能勝過「理」，這是當然的。<br />\n<br />\n理，不能勝過「法」。例如，在法官之前，即使你講說多少道理，但是他也可能說：「我知道你有很多的理由，不過你做的這件事情不合法。」所以，在法律之前，道理也不算道理了。<br />\n<br />\n法，不能勝過「權」。例如，古代有權勢的人，他可以改變法令。就是今日，世界上也還有許多地方只講權力，沒有法制。<br />\n<br />\n權，不能勝過「天」。天，就是最高的真理，也就是因果的道理。一個人權力再大，就算是逃脫得了法律的制裁，但是在因果、天理之前，必定也要受報。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">汝欲和平，必先備戰<br />\n替天行道</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"e4f60d95cf68e78429835574b86b56e70c07384f","tid":1569644,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[澄清]國難五金課金問題&mdash;照舊課！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n國難五金專訪 [開鋪事直請留意國難五金FB]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"}]}